   fix.

   render the circuit, ensuring all necessary files are present on the

   specifically simulate and verify this scenario.

title: refactor
description: Refactors the codebase to improve modularity by breaking down large files and functions into smaller, more focused units.
body:
This pull request refactors the codebase to improve modularity, primarily by breaking down large files and functions  
into smaller, more focused units.                                                                                     

The key changes are:                                                                                                  

  Simulation Logic Refactoring: In simulateAC.ts and simulateTRAN.ts, complex logic for building linear systems and  
   stamping components has been extracted from the main simulation loops into dedicated helper functions like         
   buildLinearSystemForAC and stampAllElementsAtTime.                                                                 
  Parser Modularization: The large parseNetlist.ts file has been split. Helper utilities are now in new, dedicated   
   files:                                                                                                             
     lib/parsing/NodeIndex.ts                                                                                        
     lib/parsing/units.ts                                                                                            
     lib/parsing/waveforms.ts                                                                                        
  Constants and Types:                                                                                               
     A new file lib/constants/physics.ts is introduced to centralize physical constants like VT_300K (thermal        
      voltage).                                                                                                       
     An empty file lib/types/simulation.ts was added, likely for future use.
